<!--- Guidance for Administrator references screen --->

<ul>

<li>The text that the user sees on the <strong>References</strong> screen is authored by you, the Administrator.  You will enter that text here.</li>

<li>On the <strong>References</strong> screen, you can provide the user with links to <strong>external</strong> documents and websites.  (Internally-housed documents that users have uploaded into the Planning Tool are listed & accessed on the <strong>Document Summary</strong> screen.)</li>

<li>The entry-box provides many formatting options.  As you do your entries, check the outcome on the <strong>References</strong> screen.</li>

<li>As you type inside the entry-box, [Enter] creates a new paragraph preceded by a space. [Shift-Enter] creates a new paragraph with no intervening space.</li>


</ul>